{"tid":1301681,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"去遊行既話 順手幫果個地方既連儂牆擴建 麻煩大家!!","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T02:59:23.000Z","uid":134773,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea105b142479fee5d2546d728aa6aac4d70762b","tid":1301681,"uid":134773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"連儂牆要做到好似大埔成條隧道咁，要夠多有心人幫手，夠大幅牆，夠多人貼，又要頂得住廢老搞破壞，所以唔係區區搞得成或者hold得耐<br />\n<br />\n黎緊有上水同沙田既遊行，由其上水廢老多內地人出入多既地方，希望當日可以借呢個機會整到幅夠大既連儂牆，等個邊啲人可以更了解我地既團結同訴求，政府既不堪，警權過大等資訊<br />\n<br />\n所以希望借住個勢，當日遊行會有大量同路人出入既時候，順便幫手擴建連儂牆，由其上水呢啲地方唔夠力好難造得起，大家幫幫忙,當然沙田都要<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫推thx"},{"pid":"75f6c3154ba0e4dec439b0d9b9c048303cd5df69","tid":1301681,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>TVB港姐</ins> - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n<strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=07dc1a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=c7e4a178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<strong>7.12</strong> - <ins>光復港大 守衛我城</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=02f9892a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n<strong>7.13</strong> - <ins>光復上水</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=